with top_periods as (
    select
        ID,

        CAOP_IND,
        ARRAY_AGG(OBJECT_CONSTRUCT(

    where HEENWEG_REGELTYPE = 'P' 
    group by ID, TOP_ID, CAOP_IND   
)
-- Tweede CTE: Voegt TOP's en hun geassocieerde periodes samen in een array van objecten
, tops_with_periods as (
    select 
        t.ID,
        ARRAY_AGG(OBJECT_CONSTRUCT(
            'top_id', tp.TOP_ID,
            'caop_ind', tp.CAOP_IND,
            'periods', tp.PERIODS
        )) as TOPS
    from CDWH_5_INF_CLS.INF_CLS_EXPORT_PPM_ENDSTATE_VW t
        join TOP_PERIODS tp 
            on t.ID = TP.ID 
    where t.HEENWEG_REGELTYPE = 'T' 
    group by t.ID, t.TOP_ID
) 
-- Derde CTE: Maakt objecten met hun attributen en geassocieerde TOP's
, objects_with_tops AS (
    select --TOP 100
        o.ID,
        OBJECT_CONSTRUCT(
            'obj_type', OBJ_TYPE,
            'status', STATUS,
            'name', NAME,
            'description', DESCRIPTION,
            'plant', PLANT,

            'knelpuntcode', KNELCOD,
            'cbscode', CBSCOD,
            'prog_id', PROG_ID,
          	'samenwerkvorm', SAMENWERKINGSVORM,
          	'oam_soort', OAM_SOORT
        ) as ATTR,
        t.TOPS,
        ROW_NUMBER() over (partition by o.ID order by o.ID) as regelnummer
    from CDWH_5_INF_CLS.INF_CLS_EXPORT_PPM_ENDSTATE_VW o
      	left join tops_with_periods t 
            on o.ID = t.ID 
    where o.HEENWEG_REGELTYPE = 'O' 
    qualify regelnummer = 1
) 
-- Hoofdquery: Maakt de uiteindelijke output JSON
select
